topLevelComment.author: BalanceIT
topLevelComment.text: Great videos. In this one though, are you sure U is a subset of A? You say it's a superset of A at the end, which makes sense, but I can't see how it's a subset (maybe a non-proper subset, since it's equal).

replies.author: Salem Ouail
replies.text:
You can say both
U super set of A
Or U sub set of A
Basically  because  they  are equal
